<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-zinc-100 text-[11px] font-bold text-zinc-700 uppercase">Node.js</span>
<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-zinc-100 text-[11px] font-bold text-zinc-700 uppercase">AWS Lambda</span>
</div>
<div class="bg-[#F3F3F3] p-6 border-l-4 border-black italic text-sm text-zinc-700 mb-4">"The engineering quality provided by Web Agency Inc allowed us to scale our operations globally within months. A truly world-class partner."<br>
<span class="not-italic font-bold text-black mt-2 block">— Marcus Chen, CTO at SwiftTrack</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class="group cursor-pointer">
<div class="overflow-hidden bg-zinc-100 aspect-[16/10] mb-8 relative rounded-lg">
