</div>
<a href="#" id="project-2-link" class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full border border-zinc-200 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-black group-hover:text-white transition-all">
<iconify-icon icon="lucide:arrow-up-right" class="text-xl">
</iconify-icon>
</a>
</div>
<p class="text-zinc-600 mb-6">Multi-tenant rental marketplace supporting 50+ languages and dynamic pricing engines for localized markets.</p>
<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-8">
<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-zinc-100 text-[11px] font-bold text-zinc-700 uppercase">Next.js</span>
<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-zinc-100 text-[11px] font-bold text-zinc-700 uppercase">PostgreSQL</span>
<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-zinc-100 text-[11px] font-bold text-zinc-700 uppercase">Redis</span>
</div>
<div class="bg-[#F3F3F3] p-6 border-l-4 border-black italic text-sm text-zinc-700 mb-4">"The localized booking flows resulted in a 40% increase in cross-border reservations in just the first quarter."<br>
<span class="not-italic font-bold text-black mt-2 block">— Elena Rodriguez, Product Lead</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class="group cursor-pointer">
<div class="overflow-hidden bg-zinc-100 aspect-[16/10] mb-8 relative rounded-lg">
<img src="https://pquxfbbxflqvtidtlrhl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/hmac-uploads/brand/aa611a48-0f31-4fc3-91b8-a97e15fbee97/assets/cd41ecf3-24c9-407d-8b6f-51ed14683272.webp" alt="Fintech App" class="project-image w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700">
</div>
<div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4 mb-4">
<div class="space-y-1">
<div class="text-[10px] font-bold text-[#276EF1] uppercase tracking-widest">Fintech & Banking</div>
<h3 class="text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight-uber">Vertex Capital Portal</h3>
</div>
<a href="#" id="project-3-link" class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full border border-zinc-200 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-black group-hover:text-white transition-all">
<iconify-icon icon="lucide:arrow-up-right" class="text-xl">
</iconify-icon>
</a>
</div>
