</div>
<div class="bg-[#F3F3F3] p-6 border-l-4 border-black italic text-sm text-zinc-700 mb-4">"The speed of the headless site combined with AR features drove our engagement rates through the roof."<br>
<span class="not-italic font-bold text-black mt-2 block">— Sarah L., Digital Director</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<section id="contact" class="px-6 py-24 bg-black text-white">
<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
<h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold tracking-tight-uber mb-8">Your vision, our <span class="text-[#276EF1]">engineering.</span>
</h2>
<p class="text-xl text-zinc-400 mb-12">Join our roster of successful clients and build something remarkable.</p>
<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-6">
<a href="https://draft-e11fecc2-0b32-4174-ab08-ccd3c29b1ab1.preview.superdesign.dev" id="cta-primary-btn" class="bg-white text-black px-12 py-5 text-lg font-bold hover:bg-zinc-200 transition-all w-full sm:w-auto">Start a Project</a>
<a href="https://draft-6895e637-8acf-4f1b-b88e-5bad8392c4c2.preview.superdesign.dev" id="cta-secondary-btn" class="bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-700 text-white px-12 py-5 text-lg font-bold hover:bg-zinc-800 transition-all w-full sm:w-auto">Our Services</a>
